{
  "stem": "7282.2",
  "chunk_idx": 0,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "In 1939, it was, like, [PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] the Polish and German war.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It started in '39.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "During that period, in '39, [PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] it was-- like I, I-- the, the, the, the, the Polish government, what, and the city, like, the mayor from the city, they organized some-- [PAUSES FOR 5 SECONDS] how do you call it-- like, a militia.",
      "word_count": 46
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "It was the guard to patrol the streets, or what.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So I mean, the people, I mean, in the evenings, it was-- it wasn't any light.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "It was dark, because--",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "--the-- yeah, curfew.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Because the planes used to fly around and used to bombard there.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And so, shall you say, I, I been in patrolling the, the streets with somebody else, not by myself.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Somebody else, too, used to-- used to go, or what.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And, like, our city, Ostrog, it was-- they had a, a natural border, like a river.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "The river, its name was Vilna.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "So we used to go to the river.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And we used to see-- there-- it was the river, and it was then woods.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Through the woods, we used to see the lights from the Russian Army, moving closer, and closer, and closer.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And then, when, the-- when the Germans was to take over all Poland, they work it under-- I don't recall the, the city.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "Well, then Stalin made a pact with Hitler.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "They dividing the Poland in two parts.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "One part went to Germany.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "The other part went to Russia.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "So-- and I was on the side from Russia.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "So since '39, I been there in Russia.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "Well, in the first days, I mean, we heard a lot about it.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "But we couldn't comprehend that this is real, the way people used to tell us, or what.",
      "word_count": 17
    }
  ],
